name: Enmesher
description:
An original Gory Orgy CLASSIC animated loop. 18 seconds. 1024X1024, H264, 2021
The animation Enmesher is the result of careful data-set curation and days of machine learning processes. This is the first Gory Orgy CLASSIC loop to be available for purchase. It is an Hic Et Nunc exclusive with a limited edition of three copies, one of which will be retained by the artist. Gory Orgy is the experimental machine-learning project by kiwi artist and film-maker Ed Lust.
